snippet.title: Are YOU one of these DOTS???
snippet.description:
What's your ideal Friday night? In this video I take a look at where the parties are at!

I make all of my charts from scratch with open data sets. Here's where I got the NYC noise complaints data: https://www.kaggle.com/somesnm/partynyc/data

SMASH that like button and subscribe if you like my videos! I try to get creative with the data that I find and try to tell a story with it. 

If you're new to my channel, I do data storytelling :) Hope you enjoyed!
